-- Piramal to Pay Bonus to Employees After Abbott Deal, Economic Times Says
-- Anoop Agrawal
-- 2010-06-23T01:21:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/piramal-to-pay-bonus-to-employees-after-selling-unit-to-abbott-times-says.html

          
          
             Piramal Healthcare Ltd. will pay a
cash bonus to more than 8,000 employees after selling its
formulations business to U.S. drugmaker Abbott Laboratories, the
Economic Times newspaper reported, citing an e-mail sent by
chairman Ajay Piramal to the staff.  
